overview: It’s the first night at Camp Bareback and best friends Dakota Lovell and Jack Andram decide to separate from the group to set up camp by themselves. Scout master Joshua Kelly goes over the uniform inspection with boy scouts Dakota Lovell and Jack Andram. Scout leader Greg McKeon welcomes new scout boy Cyrus Stark into camp, submitting him to the required orientation. Cute scout Dakota Lovell walks in on scoutmaster Aiden Asher as he’s hanging out in his tent, he asks him if he could help him do something manly so he can earn his “wood working” boadge and scoutmaster Aiden happily agrees.
title: Camp Bareback Boys
